![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/889b5c7a-f287-47c8-b679-b3aff7cc2325/28047.jpg)

Ilja Dragunov has finally been defeated in his United States Open Challenge.

Caramelo Hayes defeated Dragunov at the WWE Smackdown/RAW tapings in Grand Rapids, MI to become the new United States Champion.

The title change will air next week on Smackdown.